channel.title: Port Forwarding problem
channel.description:
I have a Dlink DI-524 wireless router and I seem to have problems finding my private ip so I can portforward.
Is it the default gateway (192.168.0.1) or my computers ip (how do I figure that out?), or is it a different ip, and what is it?
Also, if you have a no-ip ready so people can log in to your server, can you log in using the no-ip to test if it works?
Help is greatly appreciated.
